<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

  <title>Prelude</title>

  <style>
    :root {
      --coral: #FF6F61;
      --lavender: #B3AEDF;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(255,111,97,0.25), transparent 65%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(122,95,255,0.25), transparent 65%),
        linear-gradient(160deg, #05070D, #0A0F1F, #1C2541);
      color: var(--lavender);
      font-family: "Cormorant Garamond", serif;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-y: auto;
      scrollbar-width: none;
      -ms-overflow-style: none;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
    }

    body::-webkit-scrollbar {
      display: none;
    }

    /* Notes cluster — identical to index */
    .note-cluster {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.35rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .note {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      color: var(--lavender);
      text-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(199,196,226,0.7);
    }

    /* Title — identical to index */
    .title {
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,111,97,0.85);
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      position: relative;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .title::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
      width: 150%;
      height: 150%;
      background: radial-gradient(
        circle,
        rgba(255,111,97,0.18),
        rgba(255,111,97,0.05) 60%,
        transparent 80%
      );
      filter: blur(18px);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    /* Content wrapper */
    .content-wrapper {
      max-width: 700px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding-bottom: 6rem;
    }

    .content {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.55;
      color: var(--lavender);
      text-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }

    /* Signature container stays block-level for alignment */
    .signature {
      display: block;
      width: 100%;
      text-align: right;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    /* Inline element handles hover/touch */
    .signature span {
      display: inline-block;
      color: rgb(154, 154, 203);
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;

      /* subtle default glow */
      text-shadow: 0 0 4px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);

      transition: color 0.25s ease, text-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
    }

    /* Laptop hover */
    .signature span:hover {
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    /* Phone tap */
    .signature span:active {
      color: var(--coral);
      text-shadow: 0 0 14px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    /* ⭐ Mobile-only stronger ambient glow */
    @media (hover: none) and (pointer: coarse) {
      .signature span {
        text-shadow:
          0 0 8px rgba(199,196,226,0.55),
          0 0 14px rgba(199,196,226,0.35),
          0 0 20px rgba(199,196,226,0.25);
      }
    }

    /* Bottom-left link */
    .home-link {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 1.2rem;
      left: 1.2rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--coral);
      padding: 0.45rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,111,97,0.45);
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255,111,97,0.55);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.6px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
      transition: background 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    .home-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .home-link:active {
      background: rgba(255,111,97,0.25);
      box-shadow: 0 0 16px rgba(255,111,97,0.75);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="note-cluster">
    <div class="note">♫</div>
    <div class="note">♪</div>
    <div class="note">♫</div>
  </div>

  <div class="title">Prelude</div>

  <div class="content-wrapper">

    <div class="content">
      <p>
        Instrumental Notes is a website that brings together musical instruments from different cultures and traditions. Each instrument that is represented here is accompanied by the sound it produces, further enriched by the culture surrounding it, the people playing it and the music it features in. This is a way to appreciate such instruments by being able to both interact with them and reflect upon them.
      </p>
    </div>

    <a class="signature" href="https://github.com/musman-uk" target="_blank">
      <span>Mohammed Usman</span>
    </a>

  </div>

  <a class="home-link" href="/">Instrumental Notes</a>

</body>
</html>
